# To run automation testing on a real device
Start your Android device.

Tap Settings, and then General About Device.

Tap the Build number seven times to enable Developer option.

Return to the Settings menu and select Developer option.

Tap the Developer options to turn on USB Debugging from the menu on the next screen.

Also when connect the device, make sure the dialog to approve for debug, so the device will show from adb devices command

# ADB
tt0622@WH04VVD4JH G7X_Tests % adb devices

# Install apk
adb install ~/Downloads/g7.apk


